{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.5.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.5.1","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 5:1","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.004.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.005.002,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.5.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Ainsi fut achev\u00e9 tout l\u2019ouvrage que Salomon fit pour la maison de l\u2019\u00c9ternel. Puis il apporta l\u2019argent, l\u2019or et tous les ustensiles que David, son p\u00e8re, avait consacr\u00e9s, et il les mit dans les tr\u00e9sors de la maison de Dieu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.5","name":"2 Chroniques 5","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.5.2","name":"2 Chroniques 5:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.5.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.4.22","name":"2 Chroniques 4:22","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.4.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.5.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.5.2","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 5:2","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.005.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.005.003,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">D\u00e9dicace du temple<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 2-14: cf. 1 R 8:1-11. 1 Ch 15.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.5.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Alors Salomon assembla \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem les anciens d\u2019Isra\u00ebl et tous les chefs des tribus, les chefs de famille des enfants d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, pour transporter de la cit\u00e9 de David, qui est Sion, l\u2019arche de l\u2019alliance de l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.5","name":"2 Chroniques 5","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.5.3","name":"2 Chroniques 5:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.5.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.5.1","name":"2 Chroniques 5:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.5.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.5.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.5.3","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 5:3","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.005.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.005.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.5.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Tous les hommes d\u2019Isra\u00ebl se r\u00e9unirent aupr\u00e8s du roi pour la f\u00eate, qui se c\u00e9l\u00e9bra le septi\u00e8me mois.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.5","name":"2 Chroniques 5","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.5.4","name":"2 Chroniques 5:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.5.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.5.2","name":"2 Chroniques 5:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.5.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.5.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.5.4","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 5:4","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.005.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.005.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.5.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Lorsque tous les anciens d\u2019Isra\u00ebl furent arriv\u00e9s, les L\u00e9vites port\u00e8rent l\u2019arche.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.5","name":"2 Chroniques 5","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.5.5","name":"2 Chroniques 5:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.5.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.5.3","name":"2 Chroniques 5:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.5.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.5.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.5.5","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 5:5","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.005.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.005.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.5.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Ils transport\u00e8rent l\u2019arche, la tente d\u2019assignation, et tous les ustensiles sacr\u00e9s qui \u00e9taient dans la tente: ce furent les sacrificateurs et les L\u00e9vites qui les transport\u00e8rent.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.5","name":"2 Chroniques 5","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.5.6","name":"2 Chroniques 5:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.5.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.5.4","name":"2 Chroniques 5:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.5.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.5.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.5.6","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 5:6","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.005.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.005.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.5.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Le roi Salomon et toute l\u2019assembl\u00e9e d\u2019Isra\u00ebl convoqu\u00e9e aupr\u00e8s de lui se tinrent devant l\u2019arche. Ils sacrifi\u00e8rent des brebis et des b\u0153ufs, qui ne purent \u00eatre ni compt\u00e9s, ni nombr\u00e9s, \u00e0 cause de leur multitude.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.5","name":"2 Chroniques 5","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.5.7","name":"2 Chroniques 5:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.5.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.5.5","name":"2 Chroniques 5:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.5.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.5.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.5.7","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 5:7","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.005.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.005.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.5.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Les sacrificateurs port\u00e8rent l\u2019arche de l\u2019alliance de l\u2019\u00c9ternel \u00e0 sa place, dans le sanctuaire de la maison, dans le lieu tr\u00e8s saint, sous les ailes des ch\u00e9rubins.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.5","name":"2 Chroniques 5","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.5.8","name":"2 Chroniques 5:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.5.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.5.6","name":"2 Chroniques 5:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.5.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.5.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.5.8","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 5:8","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.005.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.005.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.5.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Les ch\u00e9rubins avaient les ailes \u00e9tendues sur la place de l\u2019arche, et ils couvraient l\u2019arche et ses barres par-dessus.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.5","name":"2 Chroniques 5","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.5.9","name":"2 Chroniques 5:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.5.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.5.7","name":"2 Chroniques 5:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.5.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.5.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.5.9","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 5:9","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.005.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.005.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.5.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>On avait donn\u00e9 aux barres une longueur telle que leurs extr\u00e9mit\u00e9s se voyaient \u00e0 distance de l\u2019arche devant le sanctuaire, mais ne se voyaient point du dehors. L\u2019arche a \u00e9t\u00e9 l\u00e0 jusqu\u2019\u00e0 ce jour.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.5","name":"2 Chroniques 5","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.5.10","name":"2 Chroniques 5:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.5.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.5.8","name":"2 Chroniques 5:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.5.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.5.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.5.10","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 5:10","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.005.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.005.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.5.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Il n\u2019y avait dans l\u2019arche que les deux tables que Mo\u00efse y pla\u00e7a en Horeb, lorsque l\u2019\u00c9ternel fit alliance avec les enfants d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, \u00e0 leur sortie d\u2019\u00c9gypte.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.5","name":"2 Chroniques 5","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.5.11","name":"2 Chroniques 5:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.5.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.5.9","name":"2 Chroniques 5:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.5.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.5.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.5.11","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 5:11","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.005.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.005.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.5.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Au moment o\u00f9 les sacrificateurs sortirent du lieu saint, car tous les sacrificateurs pr\u00e9sents s\u2019\u00e9taient sanctifi\u00e9s sans observer l\u2019ordre des classes,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.5","name":"2 Chroniques 5","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.5.12","name":"2 Chroniques 5:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.5.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.5.10","name":"2 Chroniques 5:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.5.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.5.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.5.12","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 5:12","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.005.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.005.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.5.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>et tous les L\u00e9vites qui \u00e9taient chantres, Asaph, H\u00e9man, Jeduthun, leurs fils et leurs fr\u00e8res, rev\u00eatus de byssus, se tenaient \u00e0 l\u2019orient de l\u2019autel avec des cymbales, des luths et des harpes, et avaient aupr\u00e8s d\u2019eux cent vingt sacrificateurs sonnant des trompettes,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.5","name":"2 Chroniques 5","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.5.13","name":"2 Chroniques 5:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.5.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.5.11","name":"2 Chroniques 5:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.5.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.5.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.5.13","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 5:13","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.005.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.005.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.5.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>et lorsque ceux qui sonnaient des trompettes et ceux qui chantaient, s\u2019unissant d\u2019un m\u00eame accord pour c\u00e9l\u00e9brer et pour louer l\u2019\u00c9ternel, firent retentir les trompettes, les cymbales et les autres instruments, et c\u00e9l\u00e9br\u00e8rent l\u2019\u00c9ternel par ces paroles: Car il est bon, car sa mis\u00e9ricorde dure \u00e0 toujours! En ce moment, la maison, la maison de l\u2019\u00c9ternel fut remplie d\u2019une nu\u00e9e.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.5","name":"2 Chroniques 5","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.5.14","name":"2 Chroniques 5:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.5.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.5.12","name":"2 Chroniques 5:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.5.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.5.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.5.14","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 5:14","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.005.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.006.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.5.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Les sacrificateurs ne purent pas y rester pour faire le service, \u00e0 cause de la nu\u00e9e; car la gloire de l\u2019\u00c9ternel remplissait la maison de Dieu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.5","name":"2 Chroniques 5","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.6.1","name":"2 Chroniques 6:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.6.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.5.13","name":"2 Chroniques 5:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.5.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fb957a5b1.84490085');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb957a5b1.84490085\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fb957a5b1.84490085","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fb957a5b1.84490085'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb957a5b1.84490085\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}